translations: adj．皱褶的，起皱的：指布料、纸张等表面出现皱褶或不平整的状态。
· The bedsheet was rucked up after a restless night.
经过一个不安的夜晚，床单变得皱巴巴的。

sentences.sentence: Your dress is rucked up at the back.
sentences.translation: 你的连衣裙后面起褶儿了。

sentences.sentence: This page is wet and rucked up.
Thesheets on my bed have rucked up.
sentences.translation: 我床上的床单有褶子了。
